# Workflow

Remember. Workflow is:

1. enter email → CREATION
2. confirm email + COMPOSE DOSSIER → CONFIRME
3. click confirm button → PREINSCRIPTION
...
4. Send advance → VALID
5. Pay + all attachments → COMPLETE
...
6. Cancel → CANCELED

